{"tid":344040,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普警告巴塞：古天奴不會是巴塞拼圖","createTime":"2017-08-02T03:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T07:00:31.000Z","uid":49279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22968bf5ade811a4a931f0f2796a84ab5b6f071a","tid":344040,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"高普再次重申古天奴是非賣品，強調巴塞隆拿不要癡心妄想買人。<br />\n<br />\n紅軍已經拒絕巴塞出價7200萬鎊買入古天奴，他強調古天奴絕對不會放售，幾多錢也不願放人。<br />\n<br />\n在慕尼黑的奧迪盃比賽記者會上，高普重申球會立場。<br />\n<br />\n「古天奴是非賣品，這句話不需要再有任何解釋，這件事情已經不是新聞了，對嗎？」高普警告道。"},{"pid":"91bbca7443f46d88cf5b1352f5ee374b32a73718","tid":344040,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:41:36.000Z","msg":"未到價"},{"pid":"3498cfe6d3605419990bbb59b7c43b3ef758fc96","tid":344040,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"猁狗既轉會鳩普好似冇say 高層話晒事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee8eaa1312c85f446628e33b1be34f26d879a55","tid":344040,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未到價</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好像Rb咁<br />\n應該唔該"},{"pid":"cb2c20fe4562537c8dc18855e982a84f0a91bcb3","tid":344040,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"72m 點買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賣尼馬 用120m就有機會"},{"pid":"fa01b2b7c012e2638fa50f0ba39bba10106a0d9f","tid":344040,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:52:16.000Z","msg":"Good，高普頂實"},{"pid":"e7b3bbc8794dda8dfcefd3a2a9dac80c47d3affb","tid":344040,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>72m 點買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賣尼馬 用120m就有機會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n120m 都應該唔會賣<br />\n<br />\n依家係賣方市場 (市場太多錢 1.支那米蘭大手入貨  2. 中東油王 3. 英超新轉播費)<br />\n<br />\n有錢買唔到勁人<br />\n<br />\n摩納哥 被全歐洲分屍 因為佢係少數又勁又肯賣人<br />\n<br />\n利70m 想係rb 買 keita都 reject"},{"pid":"2896c3675a401d9a40467d5f5a94af7c7a8c3919","tid":344040,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:22:38.000Z","msg":"巴狗會覺得比幾年前 難買人左好多<br />\n(其實一堆球會都係 講價耐左 轉會時間耐左)<br />\n<br />\n本質上 <br />\n只要對比 5年前 buying club , selling club ratio <br />\n同依家 buying club, selling club ratio 就明<br />\n<br />\n單單 有錢買人/ 唔太積極賣人<br />\n就多左 差唔多成倍<br />\n<br />\n意甲 雙米蘭 (支國入資)<br />\n<br />\n德甲 Rb 多仔<br />\n (以前除左拜仁 成個德甲根本任買)<br />\n<br />\n英超 <br />\n曼(費格遜時代 其實買人唔太積極....)<br />\n利 阿 呢2隊財力大幅好轉<br />\n<br />\n已經唔講支那聯賽 都不停係度入貨"},{"pid":"9169a555d673c631f5e772a3eeff72da46dd6a8d","tid":344040,"uid":33660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"想買古仔? 得 3億咪賣比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6ce46027f155ccbe8bfd5f6c98cb9ec41b173b","tid":344040,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想買古仔? 得 3億咪賣比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利狗要錢托咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b91f34ef2da2bdd01b5c51bfb08d90f3cd6e56","tid":344040,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"仲以為佢真係話coutinho is not a puzzle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061292b77485ef193fe2d763bed4331ca0ea4ae4","tid":344040,"uid":1996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想買古仔? 得 3億咪賣比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利狗要錢托咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪又係攞去買遊艇<img src=\"/assets/